# MVP scope guard

Source of truth: `docs/MVP-PLAN.md`.

**Defer unless explicitly requested:**

- Candidate Supabase Auth / passwords
- Public open intake at `/` (invite links only)
- Virus scan, rate limits, camera capture, duplicate detection
- Recruiter notes, candidate self-serve login

**In scope:** invite-gated intake, parse + wizard, hospital search, DOCX export, admin hub, confirmation email (Resend).

If a request expands scope, call it out and propose phased delivery (see phase-labeling rule).
